</div><div></div></div></div><div id="fsNews" class="fsNews"><div class="fsNews__legal"></div><section class="wcl-section_ZO0aC wcl-section--news_uwrIN" data-testid="wcl-section"><article class="fp-article_6cT1P fp-large_-EvuA" data-analytics-context="widget-news-article" itemScope="" itemType="https://schema.org/Article" data-testid="fp-newsArticle"><link itemProp="mainEntityOfPage" itemScope="" itemType="https://schema.org/WebPage" itemID="https://www.flashscore.co.uk/news/football-premier-league-premier-league-fixtures-2025-26-all-key-games-and-dates-announced/Qeen85oC/"/><div itemProp="publisher" itemScope="" itemType="https://schema.org/Organization"><meta itemProp="name" content="Flashscore"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.flashscore.co.uk/"/><meta itemProp="logo" content="https://www.flashscore.co.uk/res/_fs/image/og/flashscore.png"/></div><nav class="wcl-breadcrumbs_0ZcSd fp-breadcrumbs_11HZZ" data-testid="wcl-breadcrumbs"><ol class="wcl-breadcrumbList_lC9sI" itemScope="" itemType="https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList"><li class="wcl-breadcrumbItem_8btmf" itemProp="itemListElement" itemScope="" itemType="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-testid="wcl-breadcrumbsItem"><a href="/news/" itemProp="item" class="wcl-breadcrumbItemLabel_2QT1M wcl-link_8XuKE"><span class="wcl-bold_NZXv6 wcl-scores-overline-03_Jdp91 wcl-scores_Na715" data-testid="wcl-scores-overline-03" itemProp="name">Flashscore News</span></a><meta itemProp="position" content="1"/><svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" data-testid="wcl-icon-action-navigation-arrow-right" class="wcl-icon_WGKvC wcl-arrow_4YbE3" width="10" height="10"><path fill-rule="evenodd" class="action-navigation-arrow-right" d="M5 19.02 14.03 10 5 .98 5.98 0l10 10-10 10-.98-.98Z"></path></svg></li><li class="wcl-breadcrumbItem_8btmf" itemProp="itemListElement" itemScope="" itemType="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-testid="wcl-breadcrumbsItem"><a href="/news/football/" itemProp="item" class="wcl-breadcrumbItemLabel_2QT1M wcl-link_8XuKE"><span class="wcl-bold_NZXv6 wcl-scores-overline-03_Jdp91 wcl-scores_Na715" data-testid="wcl-scores-overline-03" itemProp="name">Football</span></a><meta itemProp="position" content="2"/><svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" data-testid="wcl-icon-action-navigation-arrow-right" class="wcl-icon_WGKvC wcl-arrow_4YbE3" width="10" height="10"><path fill-rule="evenodd" class="action-navigation-arrow-right" d="M5 19.02 14.03 10 5 .98 5.98 0l10 10-10 10-.98-.98Z"></path></svg></li><li class="wcl-breadcrumbItem_8btmf" itemProp="itemListElement" itemScope="" itemType="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-testid="wcl-breadcrumbsItem"><a href="/news/premier-league/dYlOSQODCdnS0XT8/" itemProp="item" class="wcl-breadcrumbItemLabel_2QT1M wcl-link_8XuKE"><span class="wcl-bold_NZXv6 wcl-scores-overline-03_Jdp91 wcl-scores_Na715" data-testid="wcl-scores-overline-03" itemProp="name">Premier League</span></a><meta itemProp="position" content="3"/><svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" data-testid="wcl-icon-action-navigation-arrow-right" class="wcl-icon_WGKvC wcl-arrow_4YbE3" width="10" height="10"><path fill-rule="evenodd" class="action-navigation-arrow-right" d="M5 19.02 14.03 10 5 .98 5.98 0l10 10-10 10-.98-.98Z"></path></svg></li><li class="wcl-breadcrumbItem_8btmf" itemProp="itemListElement" itemScope="" itemType="https://schema.org/ListItem" data-testid="wcl-breadcrumbsItem"><span class="wcl-bold_NZXv6 wcl-scores-overline-03_Jdp91 wcl-scores_Na715 wcl-breadcrumbItemLabel_2QT1M" data-testid="wcl-scores-overline-03" itemProp="name">Premier League fixtures 2025/26: All key games and dates announced</span><meta itemProp="position" content="4"/></li></ol></nav><div class="wcl-NewsDetailHeadline_Gotju fp-headline_gfnLQ" data-testid="wcl-newsDetailHeadline"><h1 class="wcl-news-heading-01_XI8EP fp-title_9WuNJ" data-testid="wcl-news-heading-01" role="heading" itemProp="headline">Premier League fixtures 2025/26: All key games and dates announced</h1><div class="wcl-metaGroup_TZn2w" data-testid="wcl-newsMetaGroup"><div class="wcl-metaInfo_7JoZH"><div class="wcl-newsMeta_FQZvT" data-testid="wcl-newsMetaInfo"><span class="wcl-news-caption-01_M-eZK" data-testid="wcl-news-caption-01" itemProp="author" itemType="https://schema.org/Person" itemScope=""><span itemProp="name">Ali Pollock</span></span><meta itemProp="datePublished" content="2025-06-18T08:05:20.000Z" data-testid="wcl-newsMetaInfo-dateMeta"/></div></div><div><div class="wcl-badge_ZQidD wcl-alert_mJ0fe" data-testid="wcl-badgeMeta-alert" itemProp="dateModified" data-content="2025-06-18T08:25:05.000Z"><span class="wcl-news-caption-badges-03_WKsOO" data-testid="wcl-news-caption-badges-03">Updated </span></div></div></div></div><figure data-testid="wcl-newsImage" data-analytics-element="FULL_SIZE_PICTURE" data-analytics-img-id="1" class="wcl-figure_q22Zi fp-image_HRBWn"><picture class="wcl-picture_xJTTl wcl-clickable_m5LbF" data-testid="wcl-newsImage-picture"><source srcSet="https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r120xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.avif 120w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r300xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.avif 300w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r600xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.avif 600w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r900xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.avif 900w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r1200xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.avif 1200w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 1047px) 100vw, 614px"/><source srcSet="https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r120xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.webp 120w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r300xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.webp 300w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r600xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.webp 600w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r900xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.webp 900w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r1200xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.webp 1200w" type="image/webp" sizes="(max-width: 1047px) 100vw, 614px"/><source srcSet="https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r120xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.jpeg 120w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r300xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.jpeg 300w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r600xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.jpeg 600w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r900xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.jpeg 900w, https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r1200xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.jpeg 1200w" type="image/jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 1047px) 100vw, 614px"/><img crossorigin="anonymous" class="wcl-image_vG4MA wcl-imagePriority_3wjMT" decoding="sync" loading="eager" fetchPriority="high" src="https://livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz/r900xfq60/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638.jpeg" alt="The 2025/26 Premier League fixtures have been revealed" title="The 2025/26 Premier League fixtures have been revealed" itemProp="image"/></picture><figcaption class="wcl-caption_TiV-w wcl-article_4RVnB" data-testid="wcl-contentMetadata-default"><span class="wcl-scores-simple-text-01_-OvnR wcl-scores_Na715 wcl-articleAlt_3VElB" data-testid="wcl-scores-simple-text-01">The 2025/26 Premier League fixtures have been revealed</span><span class="wcl-scores-simple-text-01_-OvnR wcl-scores_Na715 wcl-credit_k9unK" data-testid="wcl-scores-simple-text-01">CARL RECINE / GETTY IMAGES EUROPE / Getty Images via AFP</span></figcaption></figure><p class="wcl-news-perex_rLbOI fp-perex_59joV" data-testid="wcl-news-perex" itemProp="description">The full fixture list for the 2025/26 Premier League season has been released as excitement builds for the new campaign.</p><div class="fp-body_9caht" itemProp="articleBody" data-testid="fp-newsArticle-body"><p>The opening weekend kicks off on Friday, August 15th, when current champions <a href="/team/liverpool/lId4TMwf/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Liverpool</a> face <a href="/team/bournemouth/OtpNdwrc/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Bournemouth</a>.</p><p><a href="/team/manchester-city/Wtn9Stg0/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Manchester City</a> will start their bid for a fifth title in six years against <a href="/team/wolves/j3Azpf5d/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Wolves</a>, while <a href="/team/arsenal/hA1Zm19f/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Arsenal</a> have been dealt an opening-day clash with <a href="/team/manchester-utd/ppjDR086/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Manchester United</a> as they look to build on a third-straight second-place finish.</p><p>For the newly promoted sides, <a href="/team/leeds/tUxUbLR2/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Leeds</a> have a tricky match with <a href="/team/everton/KluSTr9s/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Everton</a>, <a href="/team/burnley/z3dmTMMO/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Burnley</a> go head-to-head with <a href="/team/tottenham/UDg08Ohm/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Tottenham</a> and <a href="/team/sunderland/WSzc94ws/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Sunderland</a> will host <a href="/team/west-ham/Cxq57r8g/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">West Ham</a>.</p><p>Elsewhere, <a href="/team/aston-villa/W00wmLO0/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Aston Villa</a> welcome <a href="/team/newcastle/p6ahwuwJ/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Newcastle</a>, <a href="/team/crystal-palace/AovF1Mia/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Crystal Palace</a> visit <a href="/team/chelsea/4fGZN2oK/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Chelsea</a> and <a href="/team/nottm-forest/UsushcZr/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Nottingham Forest</a> host <a href="/team/brentford/xYe7DwID/" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Brentford</a>.</p><p>The final round of fixtures will be played on Sunday, May 24th, with all 20 clubs competing simultaneously as is tradition.</p><div class="ui-media__placeholder ska__di"></div><h2>Opening Day</h2><p><a href="/match/football/bournemouth-OtpNdwrc/liverpool-lId4TMwf/?mid=jqWq8sIi" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Liverpool v Bournemouth</a> (Friday, August 15th)</p><p><a href="/match/football/aston-villa-W00wmLO0/newcastle-p6ahwuwJ/?mid=CbKh6Ln4" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Aston Villa v Newcastle</a> (Saturday, August 16th)</p><p><a href="/match/football/brighton-2XrRecc3/fulham-69ZiU2Om/?mid=KON04aHG" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Brighton v Fulham</a></p><p><a href="/match/football/brentford-xYe7DwID/nottm-forest-UsushcZr/?mid=0YV82wnT" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Nottingham Forest v Brentford</a></p><p><a href="/match/football/sunderland-WSzc94ws/west-ham-Cxq57r8g/?mid=d4HvcH9j" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Sunderland v West Ham</a></p><p><a href="/match/football/burnley-z3dmTMMO/tottenham-UDg08Ohm/?mid=CCaRKK1c" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Tottenham Hotspur v Burnley</a></p><p><a href="/match/football/man-city-Wtn9Stg0/wolves-j3Azpf5d/?mid=Kx3ZIbW9" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Wolves v Manchester City</a> </p><p><a href="/match/football/chelsea-4fGZN2oK/crystal-palace-AovF1Mia/?mid=thirHx1M" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Chelsea v Crystal Palace</a> (Sunday, August 17th)</p><p><a href="/match/football/arsenal-hA1Zm19f/man-utd-ppjDR086/?mid=jRxEBGOq" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Manchester United v Arsenal</a></p><p><a href="/match/football/everton-KluSTr9s/leeds-tUxUbLR2/?mid=ngWM9fgd" data-analytics-element="ARTICLE_TEXT_LINK" data-analytics-alias="internal">Leeds v Everton</a> (Monday, August 18th)</p><div class="ui-media__placeholder ska__di"></div><h2>Final Day</h2><p>Brighton v Manchester United (All Sunday, May 24th, 2026)</p><p>Burnley v Wolves</p><p>Crystal Palace v Arsenal</p><p>Fulham v Newcastle</p><p>Liverpool v Brentford</p><p>Manchester City v Aston Villa</p><p>Nottingham Forest v Bournemouth</p><p>Sunderland v Chelsea</p><p>Tottenham Hotspur v Everton</p><p>West Ham United v Leeds United</p><div class="ui-media__placeholder ska__di"></div><h2>Boxing Day</h2><p>Arsenal v Brighton</p><p>Brentford v Bournemouth</p><p>Burnley v Everton</p><p>Chelsea v Aston Villa</p><p>Crystal Palace v Tottenham Hotspur</p><p>Liverpool v Wolves</p><p>Manchester United v Newcastle</p><p>Nottingham Forest v Manchester City</p><p>Sunderland v Leeds United</p><p>West Ham United v Fulham</p><div class="ui-media__placeholder ska__di"></div><h2>Major fixtures (all &#x27;weekend commencing&#x27;)</h2><p>Manchester City v Manchester United - September 13th</p><p>Manchester United v Manchester City - January 17th</p><p>Arsenal v Tottenham Hotspur - November 22nd</p><p>Tottenham Hotspur v Arsenal - February 21st</p><p>Chelsea v Tottenham Hotspur - May 17th</p><p>Tottenham Hotspur v Chelsea - November 1st</p><p>Liverpool v Manchester United - October 18