<script type="text/javascript">window.fsNewsData = {"data":{"articleData":{"id":"Qeen85oC","title":"Premier League fixtures 2025\/26: All key games and dates announced","perex":"The full fixture list for the 2025\/26 Premier League season has been released as excitement builds for the new campaign.","content":"[p]The opening weekend kicks off on Friday, August 15th, when current champions [a href=\"\/team\/liverpool\/lId4TMwf\/\"]Liverpool[\/a] face [a href=\"\/team\/bournemouth\/OtpNdwrc\/\"]Bournemouth[\/a].[\/p][p][a href=\"\/team\/manchester-city\/Wtn9Stg0\/\"]Manchester City[\/a] will start their bid for a fifth title in six years against [a href=\"\/team\/wolves\/j3Azpf5d\/\"]Wolves[\/a], while [a href=\"\/team\/arsenal\/hA1Zm19f\/\"]Arsenal[\/a] have been dealt an opening-day clash with [a href=\"\/team\/manchester-utd\/ppjDR086\/\"]Manchester United[\/a] as they look to build on a third-straight second-place finish.[\/p][p]For the newly promoted sides, [a href=\"\/team\/leeds\/tUxUbLR2\/\"]Leeds[\/a] have a tricky match with [a href=\"\/team\/everton\/KluSTr9s\/\"]Everton[\/a], [a href=\"\/team\/burnley\/z3dmTMMO\/\"]Burnley[\/a] go head-to-head with [a href=\"\/team\/tottenham\/UDg08Ohm\/\"]Tottenham[\/a] and [a href=\"\/team\/sunderland\/WSzc94ws\/\"]Sunderland[\/a] will host [a href=\"\/team\/west-ham\/Cxq57r8g\/\"]West Ham[\/a].[\/p][p]Elsewhere, [a href=\"\/team\/aston-villa\/W00wmLO0\/\"]Aston Villa[\/a] welcome [a href=\"\/team\/newcastle\/p6ahwuwJ\/\"]Newcastle[\/a], [a href=\"\/team\/crystal-palace\/AovF1Mia\/\"]Crystal Palace[\/a] visit [a href=\"\/team\/chelsea\/4fGZN2oK\/\"]Chelsea[\/a] and [a href=\"\/team\/nottm-forest\/UsushcZr\/\"]Nottingham Forest[\/a] host [a href=\"\/team\/brentford\/xYe7DwID\/\"]Brentford[\/a].[\/p][p]The final round of fixtures will be played on Sunday, May 24th, with all 20 clubs competing simultaneously as is tradition.[\/p][embed guid=\"b5bd4e3f-f73c-4e46-a154-34c385cadffb\" url=\"https:\/\/x.com\/premierleague\/status\/1935247866139918435\" social-type=\"twitter\" \/][h2]Opening Day[\/h2][p][a href=\"\/match\/football\/bournemouth-OtpNdwrc\/liverpool-lId4TMwf\/?mid=jqWq8sIi\"]Liverpool v Bournemouth[\/a] (Friday, August 15th)[\/p][p][a href=\"\/match\/football\/aston-villa-W00wmLO0\/newcastle-p6ahwuwJ\/?mid=CbKh6Ln4\"]Aston Villa v Newcastle[\/a] (Saturday, August 16th)[\/p][p][a href=\"\/match\/football\/brighton-2XrRecc3\/fulham-69ZiU2Om\/?mid=KON04aHG\"]Brighton v Fulham[\/a][\/p][p][a href=\"\/match\/football\/brentford-xYe7DwID\/nottm-forest-UsushcZr\/?mid=0YV82wnT\"]Nottingham Forest v Brentford[\/a][\/p][p][a href=\"\/match\/football\/sunderland-WSzc94ws\/west-ham-Cxq57r8g\/?mid=d4HvcH9j\"]Sunderland v West Ham[\/a][\/p][p][a href=\"\/match\/football\/burnley-z3dmTMMO\/tottenham-UDg08Ohm\/?mid=CCaRKK1c\"]Tottenham Hotspur v Burnley[\/a][\/p][p][a href=\"\/match\/football\/man-city-Wtn9Stg0\/wolves-j3Azpf5d\/?mid=Kx3ZIbW9\"]Wolves v Manchester City[\/a] [\/p][p][a href=\"\/match\/football\/chelsea-4fGZN2oK\/crystal-palace-AovF1Mia\/?mid=thirHx1M\"]Chelsea v Crystal Palace[\/a] (Sunday, August 17th)[\/p][p][a href=\"\/match\/football\/arsenal-hA1Zm19f\/man-utd-ppjDR086\/?mid=jRxEBGOq\"]Manchester United v Arsenal[\/a][\/p][p][a href=\"\/match\/football\/everton-KluSTr9s\/leeds-tUxUbLR2\/?mid=ngWM9fgd\"]Leeds v Everton[\/a] (Monday, August 18th)[\/p][embed guid=\"15df809b-1178-4598-93eb-6ebbe0904972\" url=\"https:\/\/x.com\/premierleague\/status\/1935248624675385592\" social-type=\"twitter\" \/][h2]Final Day[\/h2][p]Brighton v Manchester United (All Sunday, May 24th, 2026)[\/p][p]Burnley v Wolves[\/p][p]Crystal Palace v Arsenal[\/p][p]Fulham v Newcastle[\/p][p]Liverpool v Brentford[\/p][p]Manchester City v Aston Villa[\/p][p]Nottingham Forest v Bournemouth[\/p][p]Sunderland v Chelsea[\/p][p]Tottenham Hotspur v Everton[\/p][p]West Ham United v Leeds United[\/p][embed guid=\"dd21be18-a57e-4cab-9366-3320bfec39ec\" url=\"https:\/\/x.com\/premierleague\/status\/1935251546767302789\" social-type=\"twitter\" \/][h2]Boxing Day[\/h2][p]Arsenal v Brighton[\/p][p]Brentford v Bournemouth[\/p][p]Burnley v Everton[\/p][p]Chelsea v Aston Villa[\/p][p]Crystal Palace v Tottenham Hotspur[\/p][p]Liverpool v Wolves[\/p][p]Manchester United v Newcastle[\/p][p]Nottingham Forest v Manchester City[\/p][p]Sunderland v Leeds United[\/p][p]West Ham United v Fulham[\/p][embed guid=\"d83aa6d0-17fe-4d43-a5b9-7cb43370518d\" url=\"https:\/\/x.com\/premierleague\/status\/1935249734815367486\" social-type=\"twitter\" \/][h2]Major fixtures (all 'weekend commencing')[\/h2][p]Manchester City v Manchester United - September 13th[\/p][p]Manchester United v Manchester City - January 17th[\/p][p]Arsenal v Tottenham Hotspur - November 22nd[\/p][p]Tottenham Hotspur v Arsenal - February 21st[\/p][p]Chelsea v Tottenham Hotspur - May 17th[\/p][p]Tottenham Hotspur v Chelsea - November 1st[\/p][p]Liverpool v Manchester United - October 18th[\/p][p]Manchester United v Liverpool - May 2nd[\/p][p]Everton v Liverpool - April 18th[\/p][p]Liverpool v Everton - September 20th[\/p][p]Newcastle v Sunderland - March 21st[\/p][p]Sunderland v Newcastle - December 13th[\/p][p]Brighton v Crystal Palace - February 7th[\/p][p]Crystal Palace v Brighton - November 8th[\/p]","published":1750233920,"editedAt":1750235105,"credit":"Ali Pollock","url":"https:\/\/www.flashscore.co.uk\/news\/football-premier-league-premier-league-fixtures-2025-26-all-key-games-and-dates-announced\/Qeen85oC\/","metadata":[{"name":"title","value":"Premier League fixtures 2025\/26: Key dates and times"},{"name":"description","value":"The full fixture list for the 2025\/26 Premier League season has been released as excitement builds for the new campaign."}],"images":[{"variantType":1,"url":"https:\/\/livesport-ott-images.ssl.cdn.cra.cz\/47fa5f1f-410a-4e84-9542-fa3e88841638","altText":"The 2025\/26 Premier League fixtures have been revealed","credit":"CARL RECINE \/ GETTY IMAGES EUROPE \/ Getty Images via AFP"},{"variantType":4